}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{Introduction to management\'2e Managerial functions \_ planning, deciding, 
organising, motivation, leadership, control\'2e Communication, HR 
management, information and knowledge in management, identity of organisation\'2e 
Profile of manager, ethics in management and managerial styles\'2e 
Challenges of management in globalised world\'2e Development of management\'2e}\cell\row\pard
